  <bioghist id="aspace_bac27e86bb85b7d30b3fdce9e3c049a7">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Professor of Classics, Cornell University. Professor Ginsburg died in 2002.</p>  </bioghist>
  <arrangement id="aspace_f9a992c9806a1c8f1d6cb096c42ce3e6">
    <head>COLLECTION ARRANGEMENT</head>
<p>Where possible, original folder headings have been retained. The bulk of the collection consists of materials relating to a book Ginsburg was writing, including notes and drafts of chapters.</p>  </arrangement>
  <arrangement id="aspace_ac9a34f7c881aec2d04bec6524fbafe1">
    <head>SERIES LIST</head>
<p><emph render="bold"> <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="s1">Series I. Personal</ref> </emph> Boxes: 1-2This series contains materials relating to a book Ginsburg was writing. It includes research materials and drafts of certain chapters.</p><p>  <emph render="bold"> <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="s2">Series II. Book materials</ref> </emph> Boxes: 1-2This series contains materials relating to a book Ginsburg was writing. It includes research materials and drafts of certain chapters.</p><p>  <emph render="bold"> <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="s3">Series III. Other</ref> </emph> Box 2</p>  </arrangement>
  <prefercite id="aspace_2e823797c7fc9f369bd1af084a6b0128">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>Judith Ginsburg papers, #14-9-3280. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_429ebaff448224b27d257fd2367ab9f2">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Files relating to Professor Ginsburg's research and professional activities.  Includes files on the organization of the American Philological Association's Committee on Professional Matters and regarding a session on sexual harassment and the Classics profession proposed for an annual meeting of the association.  Also, items from her memorial service, including a eulogy by Cornell professors Lynne Abel, Jennifer Whiting, and Jeffrey Rusten.</p>  </scopecontent>
